<p>Dave and John are back again this week here with their first Premium show of August. As always, your two favorite geeks walk through answering some tough (but fun!) questions, then off to sharing their tips, your tips, and finally Cool Stuff Found. Don&rsquo;t miss it! Subscribe to day &mdash; just US$25 for 6 months &mdash; and you&rsquo;ll get this episode plus lots lots more.</p>
